[[File:Mermaid storage unit map.png|frame|right|The mermaid storage unit as it appeared on the official [[world map]].]]
[[File:Mermaid storage unit location.png|thumb|Its location in relation to the world map at the time it was removed.]]
The '''mermaid storage unit''' was a location in a vast ocean south of [[Great Kourend]]. It is unknown what was here, aside from the assumption that mermaids inhabited these waters.

On [[21 January]] [[2016]], the mermaid storage unit was removed from the official world map. According to Mod Ash (jokingly), the mermaid storage unit has sunk.{{CiteTwitter|author=Mod Ash|url=https://twitter.com/JagexAsh/status/689889797901520896|date=20 January 2016|archiveurl=https://archive.is/m9PXW|archivedate=30 May 2020|quote=It [The mermaid storage unit] sank.}}

